The page consists of a title (FoodLog) with a simple logo (image) and an animated text that is typed out using CSS animations. Under the animated text, we have a simple form as shown above with a few fields and a button to submit the form.
 
1. The HTML and CSS files have been created for you. The files have the basic setup code so you can start working right away.
2. In the index.html, Here is the basic structure for the markup.
Inside the body element, we have a div with class container. Everything goes inside the container.
The div with class container has three children - an h1 with the class title, a div with the class typewriter, and another div with the class form.
The title contains the title FoodLog and the image of the burger (available in the images folder) using the ::before pseudo-class.
Inside the class div with the class typewriter, we have an h1 with some text that we will be animating.
Here is the structure of the div with the class form.
---div.form
------div.column
---------div.head
------------h1.title
------------img.logo
---------form
------------input[type]=text
------------input[type]=email
------------input[type]=password
------------button[type]=submit

3. Now it is time to move on to the CSS styling. Add the styles to the body.
4. Now let's add the following classes to add styles to the title and adding the logo image.
5. Next, we define the styles for the class typewriter. This is where the animation comes in.
6. Next, we add the layout to the form and column classes.
7. Finally, style the form and the buttons according to your preferences. Feel free to use the colors of your choice.
 
All the best.  
@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap");

* {
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: "Roboto Mono", sans-serif;
}
.body {
    background: #333;
    padding-top: 5em;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
}
.container > .title {
    color: #fff;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 48px;
    text-align: center;
}
 
.container > .title::before {
    background-image: url("/images/icon.png");
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 40px;
         height: 40px;
    content: "";
    margin-right: 20px;
}

.typewriter h1 {
    color: #fff;
    font-family: monospace;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-right: 0.15em solid orange;
    white-space: nowrap;
    margin: 20px auto;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
}

.typewriter h1 {
    animation: typing 3.5s steps(19, end), blink-caret 0.5s step-end infinite;
}

@keyframes typing {
  from {
     width: 0;
  }
  to {
    width: 100%;
 }
}

@keyframes blink-caret {
  from,
  to {
    border-color: orange;
 }
  50% {
    border-color: transparent;
 }
}

.form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 50px;
    
}

.column {
    background-color: white;
    width: 300px;
    height: 500px;
    border-radius: 15px;
}

.head .title {
    color: #748194;
    font-size: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

button[type="submit"] {
    font-weight: bold;
    width: 230px;
    margin: 0 35px 20px;
    height: 45px;
    padding: 6px 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    outline: none;
    border: none;
    background: orange;
    color: white;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
input[type="text"],
input[type="email"],
input[type="password"],
input[type="number"]{
    font-weight: bold;
    width: 200px;
    margin: 0 35px 20px;
    height: 35px;
    padding: 6px 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    outline: none;
    border: none;
    background: #f6f7f9;
    color: #748194;
    font-size: 14px;
  }